      <abstract>
        <p>Photo of sterling silver computer mouse (Father's Day Pulse column) (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To make Dad ridiculously elegant in a click, L'Art de Vivre, which sells a variety of luxury items, offers a sterling silver computer mouse. Priced at $150 from www.indulge.com, the mouse works with most personal computers, and is especially good for the father who has a lot of time on his hands -- since he'll need a year's worth of elbow grease to keep the  thing polished.</p>
      </block>
